1
00:00:30,970 --> 00:00:33,310
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,330
[Episode 10: The Bloodied Arm]

3
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,240
It's already almost the third trip.

4
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,710
Lady Fufeng's secret chamber has been

5
00:00:42,710 --> 00:00:44,710
completely cleared out by Lord Bai.

6
00:00:45,670 --> 00:00:48,130
Is Lord Bai really
going to read all of these?

7
00:00:49,030 --> 00:00:51,030
He's in seclusion, studying them himself.

8
00:00:51,030 --> 00:00:54,360
He said he needs to
quickly understand all kinds of spirits.

9
00:00:55,350 --> 00:00:56,550
Learn about spirits?

10
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,880
What's the point of just reading books?

11
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,050
If I take him out for a walk,

12
00:01:00,050 --> 00:01:01,910
he'll know everything in no time.

13
00:01:02,110 --> 00:01:02,970
Hurry up and go.

14
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:03,520
No, wait.

15
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,880
I'd like to ask for some money for drinks.

16
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:08,480
Go ask him.

17
00:01:10,510 --> 00:01:11,680
Cheapskate.

18
00:01:16,070 --> 00:01:17,120
Zuiwang Tavern?

19
00:01:17,510 --> 00:01:18,310
That's right.

20
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:20,710
My Lord, did you bring enough money
with you?

21
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:21,910
Yes, I've got enough.

22
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:22,680
Good to hear.

23
00:01:22,950 --> 00:01:23,840
The Zuiwang Tavern

24
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,200
is no ordinary tavern.

25
00:01:25,230 --> 00:01:27,789
Humans and demons sit together here—
drinking and enjoying performances.

26
00:01:27,789 --> 00:01:30,070
Didn't you say you wanted
to learn about the lives of demons?

27
00:01:30,070 --> 00:01:31,710
This place is the liveliest,

28
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:33,080
and also the safest.

29
00:02:10,590 --> 00:02:11,650
Let's go sit there.

30
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,430
Nice! Nice!

31
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:23,250
Are all the performers here spirits?

32
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:24,840
Mostly demons.

33
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:27,190
After all, each of them
has their own unique tricks.

34
00:02:27,190 --> 00:02:28,850
But Lady Fufeng set the rules—

35
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,520
performing is allowed here,

36
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,390
but they must not use real demon magic,

37
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:34,630
and they're absolutely forbidden from
turning it into a way to make a fortune.

38
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:35,430
Why is that?

39
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,450
My Lord, think about it.

40
00:02:37,590 --> 00:02:39,400
If every demon stopped proper cultivation

41
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,630
and came here just to show off tricks,

42
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,910
wouldn't Yin-Yang Crossing
fall into chaos?

43
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:45,560
And once they get a taste of easy gains
from using demon powers,

44
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,150
who can guarantee

45
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:48,630
they won't start to meddle
with that evil power in the future?

46
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,630
So you see,

47
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,590
most of the performers here

48
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:52,190
are low-level demons

49
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:53,000
just trying to earn a few coins

50
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:53,710
and get by.

51
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,190
It's basically

52
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:57,430
their first job after taking human form—

53
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:58,829
seeing a bit of the world.

54
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,910
So she didn't simply
ban everything outright.

55
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,530
Instead, she allowed this corner.

56
00:03:03,530 --> 00:03:05,630
It gives them a slim chance of survival,

57
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:09,000
while also preventing them
from spreading and becoming a menace.

58
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,730
She actually understands
the art of governance.

59
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:14,560
My Lord, since we're already here,

60
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,430
have a drink.

61
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,210
Just a little drink.

62
00:03:27,290 --> 00:03:27,890
Everyone!

63
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,750
My classmate here

64
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,710
is incredibly talented.

65
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:33,630
Today, why not let him

66
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:34,910
perform a bit for everyone

67
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,079
and liven things up?

68
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,240
Alright!

69
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:40,750
Renjie, you sure know
how to have a good time.

70
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:43,630
You said you were bringing us
to see some demon shows—

71
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,700
but I never expected

72
00:03:44,700 --> 00:03:47,300
you'd also have
a whole live troupe of your own.

73
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:50,430
Li Mao, don't forget to thank Renjie

74
00:03:50,910 --> 00:03:53,000
for taking you out to see the world.

75
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:56,190
Look at them up there—

76
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:59,360
those spirits are just doing
cheap little tricks,

77
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,680
and still getting
a full house of applause.

78
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,610
-You…
-Exactly!

79
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,030
You've got extraordinary talent.

80
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:07,230
Wouldn't it be a shame to keep it hidden?

81
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,280
Why not go up

82
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,560
and put on a show
to liven things up for everyone?

83
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,190
Yeah!

84
00:04:11,190 --> 00:04:11,840
Exactly!

85
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,190
Liven things up!

86
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:16,070
Renjie, don't joke around.

87
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,630
I can't do that.

88
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:20,430
Are you really gonna
disrespect Renjie like that?

89
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,180
What do you mean you can't?

90
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,920
You were performing just fine in private—

91
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,920
now you're scared to go on stage?

92
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:32,920
Li Mao,

93
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:38,159
you used to show us tricks all the time.

94
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:42,560
Now you're backing out?

95
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,130
Don't you want to be brothers anymore?

96
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,510
Everyone!

97
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:51,920
Get up.

98
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:54,510
My classmate here is no ordinary man.

99
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,560
Let him show us a real skill—
how about it?

100
00:04:57,560 --> 00:05:00,600
Good!

101
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,510
Hurry, hurry!

102
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,620
Alright, alright!

103
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,510
Come on! Come on!

104
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:06,430
Come on!

105
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,000
Come on!

106
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,480
Move it!

107
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,720
Hurry up!

108
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,190
Show us. Come on!

109
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:12,950
Don't drag your feet!

110
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:13,480
Start already!

111
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,160
Do it!

112
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:14,870
Come on!

113
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,510
Don't be shy!

114
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,040
Li Mao, hurry up!

115
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:19,060
Start!

116
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:20,600
What are you being shy for?

117
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,070
Just do it!

118
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:21,800
Hurry up!

119
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,560
Start!

120
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,190
We're waiting!

121
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:24,870
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

122
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:25,680
Go on!

123
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,000
Show us what you've got!

124
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,260
Start already, what are you waiting for?

125
00:05:29,470 --> 00:05:30,800
We're all waiting! Hurry!

126
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,430
Yeah!

127
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:02,630
Absurd!

128
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,630
My Lord.

129
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:09,080
What?

130
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,070
He called "My Lord"? Let's go—now!

131
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,000
Go, go, go!

132
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:11,600
Move.

133
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,240
Are you alright?

134
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,630
I'm fine.

135
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,390
Hey, you...

136
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:23,120
It's fine.

137
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,310
Everyone.

138
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,210
Everyone, don't be afraid.

139
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,240
I'm a gecko spirit.

140
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,510
My arm was just cut off—

141
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,220
it'll grow back

142
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,950
tomorrow.

143
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:45,270
So please don't worry.

144
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,010
But...

145
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,540
Doesn't that hurt?

146
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,270
I'm used to it.

147
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:55,950
You brat—

148
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:59,380
since when is limb regeneration
something you show off in a performance?

149
00:06:59,380 --> 00:07:00,730
Lady Fufeng set the rules:

150
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:02,270
no bloody acts like this are allowed.

151
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,270
Did you forget already?

152
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,240
If she finds out,

153
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,800
you'll be held accountable!

154
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,800
Lady Fufeng?

155
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,650
Alright.

156
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,450
Alright.

157
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,070
I got it.

158
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,390
Please forgive me this once.

159
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,830
Just don't tell Lady Fufeng please!

160
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:16,190
Fine, fine.

161
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:16,720
Alright.

162
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,680
I'm leaving.

163
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,240
I'm leaving.

164
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:19,980
I'm leaving.

165
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,780
Alright.

166
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,160
You...

167
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,950
My Lord, this is...

168
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,870
Let's go, let's go.

169
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:41,390
Let's go drink instead—
everyone, disperse, come on!

170
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,630
Move aside.

171
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,820
This is terrifying...

172
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,390
Can one ever really

173
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,600
get used to the pain of losing an arm?

174
00:07:50,790 --> 00:07:52,040
Bad omen...

175
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,560
So many scrolls...

176
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:21,430
Why not have Xiao Hu
bring them all over at once?

177
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:24,750
He's been working cases
with me nonstop lately.

178
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,480
He hasn't really slept in days,

179
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,070
so I sent him back

180
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,240
to rest early.

181
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,800
You've set your own rules—

182
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:34,549
coming here every night
to the Xiqianhua Mansion,

183
00:08:34,549 --> 00:08:37,360
without even asking my opinion?

184
00:08:39,789 --> 00:08:41,000
Fengling said

185
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,370
that staying close to you

186
00:08:42,370 --> 00:08:44,360
helps restore
your spiritual power faster.

187
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,670
Until we find Bai Han,

188
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,460
I'll keep coming here.

189
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,160
But don't worry, My Lady—

190
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:54,270
I won't let it interfere
with official duties.

191
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:02,150
Was there bloodshed
at the county yamen today?

192
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,670
On the way here, I ran into a man

193
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,910
and helped him out.

194
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,270
A person?

195
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,660
You're sure

196
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,950
it wasn't a gecko spirit?

197
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,550
In Yin-Yang Crossing,

198
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,870
the wind can speak.

199
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,510
And it runs

200
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,150
faster than you.

201
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:26,950
Besides,

202
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,360
the wind doesn't lie to me.

203
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:33,640
My Lady, I just...

204
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,500
Afraid I'd punish him?

205
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:40,510
My Lady, he was only forced
by circumstance.

206
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,000
Since it's his first offense,

207
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,480
and he didn't cause
any major disturbance,

208
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,760
I hope you'll show leniency

209
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,440
and not pursue it.

210
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:50,880
Alright.

211
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:54,480
For your sake,

212
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,670
I'll let it go this time.

213
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:19,810
If you keep looking
so worn out like that,

214
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,740
and it actually costs you years
of your life one day—

215
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:25,640
I can't have people saying
I worked you to the bone.

216
00:10:28,450 --> 00:10:29,650
Don't worry, My Lady.

217
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:30,720
I'll leave a final note

218
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,250
saying it was my own choice,

219
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:33,970
so it won't implicate you.

220
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,560
My Lady,

221
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,030
if I stay here,

222
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,210
will your spiritual power

223
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,630
really recover faster?

224
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,530
Otherwise what?

225
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,790
Do you think I'm keeping you around

226
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:03,330
because you're exceptionally handsome
and I just want to admire you every day?

227
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,200
Five drum beats.

228
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,320
Another murder case.

229
00:11:43,270 --> 00:11:44,030
Lady Fufeng!

230
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,170
Lord Bai!

231
00:11:46,220 --> 00:11:49,850
The scene inside is truly indecent

232
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:52,790
and a defilement of the sages!

233
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:58,080
Please, please don't be startled!

234
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:06,280
This was the son of the Wang family—

235
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,320
Wang Renjie.

236
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,000
I'll bring another stool.

237
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:12,360
And these were Hu Shanming
and Han Ziliang.

238
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:16,240
All three were students from the academy!

239
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:19,870
Hu.

240
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:32,280
The three victims all show ligature marks
around the throat from cloth bindings,

241
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:36,030
with the base of the tongue protruding—

242
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:38,230
clear signs of death by strangulation.

243
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:41,690
There is also a strong smell of alcohol
on the bodies,

244
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,960
and traces of liquor
in their mouths and noses.

245
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,430
Based on this,

246
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:02,150
they were likely heavily drunk
at the time of death,

247
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:09,790
around 9 PM last night.

248
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,600
In addition, their arms

249
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:16,000
were also torn off by brute force
while they were still alive.

250
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,010
Put it straight.

251
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,920
Shall I place it here?

252
00:14:25,570 --> 00:14:27,500
The assailant subdued 3 drunk men,

253
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,640
tore off both their arms,

254
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:31,280
strangled them with cloth,

255
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,440
and then hung the bodies from the beams.

256
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,530
The killer is nearly sadistic—

257
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:43,400
this is beyond human capability.

258
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:58,550
A murder has occurred within the academy.

259
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:01,890
I ask all of you to cooperate
with the investigation.

260
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:14,290
It wasn't me.

261
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,280
No, no, not me.

262
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:28,520
Last night was the academy's rest day.

263
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:30,610
Did any of you hear anything unusual?

264
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:33,960
My Lord,

265
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,750
we all went to bed by 9 PM.

266
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:38,480
We didn't hear a thing.

267
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,330
That's impossible!

268
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:44,670
My Lord,

269
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:49,590
enexpectedly, Li Mao
didn't show up for his lesson today.

270
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:51,550
He's usually the first to arrive.

271
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,030
Li Mao?

272
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:59,800
There's no trace of corruption
flowing here.

273
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:39,990
Where is she going?

274
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:47,950
Liu Fengling,

275
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,330
what are you sneaking around here for?

276
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:59,320
Pretty impressive.

277
00:17:04,349 --> 00:17:05,810
What exactly did you find?

278
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:28,109
So it really is you!

279
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:30,040
Your arm actually grew back!

280
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:31,640
Hey, you,

281
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:32,680
wake up.

282
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,030
You're Li Mao, right?

283
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,750
What are you doing hiding here

284
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,510
instead of staying at the academy?

285
00:17:38,510 --> 00:17:42,110
I'm weak... I can't get up...

286
00:17:43,190 --> 00:17:45,720
I just wanted to rest for a bit
before moving again.

287
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:48,150
I think you just don't have the strength
to run anymore.

288
00:17:48,150 --> 00:17:49,680
You insolent wretch, Li Mao!

289
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,680
Why did you murder your classmates?

290
00:17:58,680 --> 00:17:59,210
Class...

291
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,310
The three of them

292
00:18:03,450 --> 00:18:04,440
are dead?

293
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:11,790
Since when did I say
three people were dead?

294
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,690
I haven't even drawn my blade yet!

295
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,040
What's going on here?

296
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,440
His breath is faint.

297
00:18:24,890 --> 00:18:26,830
We need to get him
to Lady Fufeng immediately,

298
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,030
or he really won't make it.

299
00:18:28,030 --> 00:18:28,750
Wake up!

300
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:30,240
Why is this demon

301
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:31,720
as fragile as paper?

302
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:33,510
Wake up!

303
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:37,280
How can you just pass out like that?

304
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:39,440
Li Mao!

305
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:54,040
Overwhelmed by fear.
His mind is in disarray.

306
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,510
I've used my spiritual power
to stabilize his heart meridian.

307
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,970
He's not in danger for now.

308
00:18:58,510 --> 00:19:00,440
Thanks for your hard work, My Lady.

309
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,330
Lord Bai, you're not in such a hurry

310
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:10,110
to lock the demon culprit
in the county jail this time, are you?

311
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:13,310
My Lady, last time the mirror spirit
went out of control in the county yamen...

312
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,570
If it weren't for your intervention,

313
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:16,090
the consequences would've
been unimaginable.

314
00:19:16,090 --> 00:19:18,690
We can't let incidents like that
happen again.

315
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:21,310
Lord Bai,
you are becoming increasingly adept

316
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:23,170
at governing Yin-Yang Crossing.

317
00:19:24,360 --> 00:19:27,250
I can't keep dragging you down.

318
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:31,870
What is it?

319
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,160
It's nothing.

320
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:36,480
My Lady.

321
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:39,640
My Lady, you don't need
to be embarrassed.

322
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,550
I'm just helping you
restore your spiritual power.

323
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:42,880
A healer's heart is like that of a parent—

324
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:44,010
there are no taboos.

325
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:48,440
I'm not the one
who's embarrassed.

326
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:50,360
Lord Bai, your face is quite red—

327
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:55,140
for someone who claims to have no taboos.

328
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:10,510
My Lady, after Li Mao lost his arm,

329
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:12,160
in such a weakened state,

330
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,320
could he still kill anyone?

331
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:17,720
A gecko spirit is a low-tier demon,

332
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:19,240
timid by nature.

333
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,240
Its only ability

334
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,030
is limb regeneration.

335
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:25,970
Last night he had already severed one arm—

336
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,330
forget killing anyone,

337
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:29,590
even climbing onto the academy's beam

338
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:31,050
would've been difficult.

339
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:34,480
My Lady, that aligns with my thoughts.

340
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,550
When Li Mao heard
his classmates were murdered,

341
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,310
he blurted out
"three of them" immediately—

342
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,830
clearly something was off.

343
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:43,440
But the killer,
after committing the murders,

344
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:45,040
carefully staged the scene.

345
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,200
That suggests

346
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:49,200
a calm and highly disciplined mind.

347
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:51,720
It's impossible he would collapse

348
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,180
just from a few questions.

349
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,920
You're right.

350
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:02,000
But there's another possibility...

351
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:05,030
Corruption.

352
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,430
Like the mirror spirit—

353
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:09,910
if he was controlled by the evil power,

354
00:21:09,910 --> 00:21:11,170
his power would surge,

355
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:13,460
and afterward he would lose his memory.

356
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:16,590
That would explain
why Li Mao

357
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:18,790
acted so differently before and after.

358
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:20,400
Well done.

359
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,830
As a reward,

360
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,670
I'll give you another clue.

361
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:30,070
Wang Renjie,

362
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:31,830
Han Ziliang,

363
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:33,960
and Hu Shanming—

364
00:21:34,060 --> 00:21:34,930
what were they

365
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,070
usually like in the academy?

366
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:41,310
Renjie was a good person.

367
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,070
He often helped classmates
copy notes

368
00:21:43,070 --> 00:21:45,030
and even treated them to snacks.

369
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,200
Yes, he had good grades,

370
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:46,830
spoke politely,

371
00:21:46,830 --> 00:21:48,000
and was decent in character.

372
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,750
Han Ziliang's family

373
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:50,310
even funded our academy's library.

374
00:21:50,310 --> 00:21:51,720
They were all very well-liked.

375
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,310
Even teachers
thought highly of them.

376
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:54,310
What about Li Mao?

377
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:58,440
Did he have any conflicts
with the three victims?

378
00:21:58,680 --> 00:22:00,550
We're not really sure.

379
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:01,880
Not sure?

380
00:22:02,350 --> 00:22:03,550
This is a murder case!

381
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:06,960
Withholding information
is punishable by law!

382
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:08,750
Well...

383
00:22:09,750 --> 00:22:12,010
Sir, why make things difficult for them?

384
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,080
What could they even say?

385
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,970
Good that those three died.

386
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:18,790
They deserved to die!

387
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:29,670
Then explain—
how exactly did they deserve it?

388
00:22:30,550 --> 00:22:32,150
They relied on their wealth,

389
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,550
excelled in their studies,

390
00:22:33,550 --> 00:22:34,960
and were favored by the teachers.

391
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:37,270
But behind their backs,

392
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:40,200
they made fun of us—
lowborn demon-background students.

393
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:43,440
You sound very familiar with this Li Mao.

394
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:44,720
Are you friends?

395
00:22:47,140 --> 00:22:47,990
Friends?

396
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,600
That coward?

397
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,240
He got bullied to death

398
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,180
and didn't dare say a word.

399
00:22:53,750 --> 00:22:54,750
I look down on him.

400
00:22:58,240 --> 00:22:59,500
If you're not friends,

401
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,590
why were you rushing
to find Li Mao this morning?

402
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:03,320
Lady Fufeng.

403
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:07,880
A civet has
a naturally sharp sense of smell.

404
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,680
You smelled his blood—

405
00:23:10,310 --> 00:23:14,240
that's why you hurriedly switched form
and slipped out of the academy.

406
00:23:14,830 --> 00:23:15,590
Hu.

